### Register User
POST http://localhost:5097/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testmcp@example.com",
  "password": "Password123",
  "confirmPassword": "Password123"
}

### Login User
POST http://localhost:5097/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testmcp@example.com",
  "password": "Password123"
}

### Generate MCP Token
POST http://localhost:5097/api/users/me/mcp-tokens
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

{
  "name": "My Development Token"
}

### List MCP Tokens
GET http://localhost:5097/api/users/me/mcp-tokens
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Revoke MCP Token
DELETE http://localhost:5097/api/users/me/mcp-tokens/{{token_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}